    "31e80c8a36c7080df0f2aed73cf232b18e5cec16e5de34ad0cc76aaf0e5d2b31": {
      "text": "Well, after [player name] here was ambushed outside the temple a while back, Ivan and I decided to keep a closer eye on things.",
      "placeholders": [
